  m_text: "GOAL:\r\nCollect all green orbs by switching between two rings.\r\n\r\nCONTROLS:\r\n\u2022
    Press [Q] to move to the INNER ring (closer to center)\r\n\u2022 Press [E] to
    move to the OUTER ring (farther from center)\r\n\u2022 Click to reverse your
    orbital direction\r\n"
